/*
 *  ABSTRACT:
 *
 *      This module is the platform-specific but conditionally independent
 *      code for the XTrap extension (usually I/O or platform setup).
 *      This is shared code and is subject to change only by team approval.
 *
 *  CONTRIBUTORS:
 *
 *      Dick Annicchiarico
